CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 28, 1960, pg. 14, reads: "Ohioans Attend Dinner - Six charming Youngstown, Ohio, matrons came to Pittsburgh to attend the B. and P. dinner Sunday at the Hotel Hilton. As guests of Mr. and Mrs. H. Raymond Rice, they enjoyed a full week-end.  Left to right: Mmes. Hazel Robinson, Irene Hilson, Gertrude Johnson, Gussie Lewis, Willa Mae Huff and Haydee Huff. - Harris Photo."image published by Pittsburgh Courier with woman second from left masked.
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Hazel Robinson, unknown, Irene Hilson, Gertrude Johnson, Gussie Lewis, Willa Mae Huff, and Haydee Huff, standing in Hilton Hotel
